		<RichText x="1658" y="48" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="30" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="218" height="34" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.5019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="right" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="30" color="#ffffff">元素能量：NA</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#eeeeee" distance="10" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">太郎丸进行横、纵、旋3段攻击，横纵攻击均造成<span color="#b9b9b9">50%</span><span>伤害，旋转造成4段</span><span color="#b9b9b9">35%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">太郎丸进行冲刺攻击，持续均造成<span color="#b9b9b9">50%</span><span>伤害，冲刺命中角色即停止，接着进行旋转，造成</span><span color="#b9b9b9">100%</span><span>伤害，该技能即为砻炼剑技，反击可导致其眩晕。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="410" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">太郎丸在闲置时，总会格挡近战伤害。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="798" width="421" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">太郎丸在原地留下一个石质炸药，利用帽子迅速撤离，炸药3s后爆炸，造成<span color="#ff9999">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/太郎丸.assets/Image_14.png')" x="719" y="137">
