		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">太郎丸使用尾部抓住刀汇聚雷光，转身放出3道雷刃造成<span color="#ffacff">60%,15%,6%</span><span>伤害，该雷刃可被反击。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">太郎丸传送至玩家处，翻身使用刀刃插入地面引起落雷，造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
